	    <ul>
		<li>404 file</li>
	    </ul>
	</li>
	<li>template.php
	    <ul>
		<li>serves as the template for every new project&nbsp;</li>
		<li><strong>This file is to be included into every new projects folder created</strong></li>
		<li><span style="color:red">Add/Replace</span>:
